</p>
</div>
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Select the <code>lighthouse mimic</code> by clicking on it</li>
<li>The scenario or mimic has one input:the Sun and three outputs: Lamp, Lights and Foghorn</li>
</ul>

<div class="figure">
<p><img src="./img/flowol-lighthouse-1.PNG" alt="flowol-lighthouse-1.PNG" />
</p>
