<div id="outline-container-org89efe51" class="outline-3 gold">
<h3 id="org89efe51">Badge It - Gold</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org89efe51">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org92c8538" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org92c8538">Learning Strand: Algorithms</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-org92c8538">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>The above flowchart will make the three outputs flash on and off every two seconds</li>
<li>Your task is to create a flowhcart so that:
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>when the Sun is down(off), all the three outputs will flash</li>
<li>when the Sun is up (on), if the Lights are not on, the Foghorn should be on, and if the Lights are on, the Foghorn should be off.</li>
</ul></li>
<li>Test your flowchart by clicking on the Sun to turn it on and off.</li>
<li>Screenshot your working flowchart and upload to BTL</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>

